data.description:
Welcome to this exquisite four-bedroom, three-full-bathroom home nestled in the Brookside subdivision of Raymore, offering the perfect blend of comfort and luxury. Boasting a desirable open California split layout, this home is adorned with stunning wood floors (not hardwood) that flow throughout, lending a touch of elegance to every corner.

Each of the four generously sized bedrooms is equipped with spacious closets, ensuring ample storage space and organizational convenience for all your needs. The primary bathroom features a lavish whirlpool tub, inviting you to unwind and relax after a long day. All the windows feature beautiful custom built window treatments that allow great flexibilty for both privacy and an abundance of natural light.

With its thoughtfully designed floor plan and spacious yard complete with an inground irrigation system, this residence provides an ideal space for both relaxation and entertainment. Whether you're hosting gatherings or seeking peaceful solitude, the layout offers versatility and functionality to suit any lifestyle.

Located in the charming community of Raymore, this home combines modern comforts with convenience, promising a lifestyle of both comfort and sophistication. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning property your own and experience the beauty of living in Raymore, MO.
